org.eclipse.viatra.dse.base

Class ThreadContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.base.ThreadContext

  • public class ThreadContext
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds all the information that is related to a single processing thread of the DesignSpaceExploration process. For any attributes related to the Design Space Exploration process as a whole, see GlobalContext.
